On the right side of the image, a large tree stands tall, its leaves a vibrant splash of green against the neutral tones of the buildings. This natural element provides a stark contrast to the man-made structures, reminding us of the coexistence of nature and urban development in many cities around the world. 

Overall, the image captures a typical day on a busy street in Beijing, showcasing the city's architectural style and the daily life of its inhabitants.
